               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Iṟaiyaṉār Akapporuḷ</title>, text and commentary. The text, entitled <title xml:lang="ta">Iṟaivaṉār Akapporuḷ</title> in the manuscript, is incomplete: stops short in the commentary to <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign> 59.</p>
<p>Spaces left blank throughout as the master copy was defective.</p>

<p>No intertitles, no <foreign xml:lang="sa">pratīka</foreign>s, no illustration verses.</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (April 2019).</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>      </summary>
                  
